reviewText:
A collection of beauties from the mid '90s. I have to say that a handful of these ladies really stood out for me in this edition. Becky Delos Santos, Anna-Marie Goddard, Carrie Westcott (most definitely), Jennifer Lavoie. Julie Lynn Cialini. All of them are beautiful in their own way, but I found the aforementioned the most eye catching for me. All of them are completely nude at one point in their respective segments. Added note that this edition features two playmate of the years 1994 and 1995. Jenny and Julie. Very nice.
The quality is fairly decent and I think Image did a good job of that. Look around though for a good price at a used DVD/Book place. I did and found this for not even close to what they want on this site.
Color, 1998, 55 minutes, Chapter Selections, Rated X

The best playmate is featured ....busty Julianna Moore Nov 1993.  Also is Arlene Baxter Dec 1993 and 1994 PMOY  Jenny McCarthy.  I just did not like the editing .... too much jumping around from one scene to another.

Playboy 1995 Video Playmate Calendar is 57 minutes long and was released on video on November 16, 1994. The 1994 video calendar has a little more nudity then those that I have rated in the past, still a few of the Playmates are conservative in show their bodies like Shae Marks. Also the video calendar goes by the month the Playmates appear and not by the month that they were featured in the magazine.

Becky DelosSantos\Miss January-Brief nudity and topless scenes and more nudity at the end of segment one. Skin shots with Becky flashing her breast and a full nudity shot of her at the end of segment two.
Arlene Baxter\Miss February-full nudity in both segments, but must wait a few moments.
Julianna Young\Miss March-A few shots of full nudity and breasts in segment one and the breasts look fake. There is some more nudity in segment two.
Elke Jeinsen\Miss April-Elke is nude about 50% of the time in segment one and mainly clothed in segment two with a few moments of nudity.
Anna-Marie Goddard\Miss May (40th Anniversary Playmate)-About a minutes into segment one, Anna-Marie is fully nude. She is never really fully nude in segment two.
Jenny McCarthy\Miss June (Playmate of the Year-1994)-A little nudity in segment one and a little more in segment two.
Neriah Davis\Miss July-Neriah is nude about 15% of the time in segment one and about 60% of the time in segment two.
Jennifer Lavoie\Miss August-Most of the time Jennifer is fully nude in the gym segment and segment two as well.
Elan Carter\Miss September-Jull nudity in segment one and Elan is nude most of the time in segment.
Shae Marks\Miss October-Brief nudity and topless scenes in segment one and two.
Julie Lynn Cialini\Miss November (Playmate of the Year in 1995)-Full nudity towards the end of segment one and a little nudity in segment two.
Carrie Westcott\Miss December-Carrie is shown nude 35% of the time in segment one and all the time in segment two.

This video seems to be of a little bit higher standard in nudity where past video calendars have failed. Playboy 1995 Video Playmate Calendar gets a B.
